Document: StaticBody2D
Path: godot/classes/class_staticbody2d.rst
Summary: Properties of StaticBody2D class including angular/linear velocity and physics material override.

- constant_angular_velocity (float): Angular velocity applied to the body. Default: 0.0
- constant_linear_velocity (Vector2): Linear velocity applied to the body. Default: Vector2(0, 0)
- physics_material_override (PhysicsMaterial): Overrides the physics material for this body. Default: empty (uses default material)
